OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FHormone replacement therapy should be
OL,7,Fthe first treatment offered to women
OL,8,Fwith menopause symptoms, a health
OL,9,Fwatchdog has said after a previous
OL,10,Fdraft of its guidelines that
OL,11,Femphasised CBT sparked an outcry.
OL,13,FThe National Institute for Health and
OL,14,FCare Excellence (Nice) said "hormone
OL,15,Freplacement therapy (HRT) is the
OL,16,Fpreferred, recommended approach" for
OL,17,Fmanaging symptoms such as hot flushes,
OL,18,Finsomnia and low mood, and should be
OL,19,Foffered by GPs in discussion with
OL,20,Fpatients about the risks and benefits.
