OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FWhat is changing?
OL,8,FDraft guidance from Nice last November
OL,9,Fsuggested cognitive behavioural
OL,10,Ftherapy (CBT) ` a talking therapy
OL,11,Fwhich is designed to help people
OL,12,Fmanage their problems by changing the
OL,13,Fway they think and behave ` could be
OL,14,Foffered as an alternative or alongside
OL,15,FHRT.
