OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FThat proved controversial and Nice has
OL,7,Fnow rewritten the guidance to stress
OL,8,Fthat HRT should be the first-line
OL,9,Ftreatment, with CBT an option for
OL,10,Fwomen in addition to HRT, for people
OL,11,Fwho cannot take HRT or for those who
OL,12,Fdo not want to take it.
OL,14,FProfessor Jonathan Benger, chief
OL,15,Fmedical officer at Nice, said they
OL,16,F"worked hard to ensure that the place
OL,17,Fof CBT" is clear and "a number of
OL,18,Fchanges have been made to emphasise
OL,19,Fthat".
