OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FHe added: "We have revised the
OL,7,Fguideline to be really clear that CBT
OL,8,Fis an adjunct, it's an add-on therapy,
OL,9,Fand it can help people manage the
OL,10,Fsymptoms... in addition to HRT, or
OL,11,Fsome women may choose not to take HRT,
OL,12,For they may not be able to take HRT,
OL,13,Fand therefore that's where CBT can be
OL,14,Fuseful."
OL,16,F"But we are very keen to emphasize
OL,17,Fthat HRT is our recommended first-line
OL,18,Ftherapy for vasomotor symptoms and for
OL,19,Fsymptoms of menopause."
