OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FAccording to the NHS, the treatment
OL,7,Faddresses the loss of hormones people
OL,8,Fexperience when they go through
OL,9,Fmenopause.
OL,11,FWhen the period stops hormones like
OL,12,Festrogen and progesterone are produced
OL,13,Fin far fewer quantities.
OL,15,FWhile their primary role is to
OL,16,Fmaintain period cycles, ovulation and
OL,17,Fpregnancy, they also keep bones strong
OL,18,Fand contribute to overall health.
