OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FHRT therapy offers people hormone
OL,7,Fsupplements to replace the ones the
OL,8,Fbody no longer produces.
OL,10,FThe treatment usually lasts up to five
OL,11,Fyears but can in some instances go on
OL,12,Ffor longer.
OL,14,FIt can be administered by tablets,
OL,15,Fpatches, gels or sprays all with their
OL,16,Fown advantages and disadvantages.
