OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FMarie Anne Ledingham, consultant
OL,7,Fclinical advisor at Nice, said the
OL,8,Foriginal draft wording on CBT had
OL,9,Fproved "controversial" and a lot of
OL,10,Ftime had been spent "reviewing the
OL,11,Fwording and the placement of CBT
OL,12,Fwithin the guideline and how it ranked
OL,13,Fin relation to the other
OL,14,Frecommendations."
OL,16,FAnnouncing the draft guideline last
OL,17,FNovember, Nice said it was
OL,18,Frecommending "more treatment choices
OL,19,Ffor menopause symptoms" and CBT
OL,20,F"should be considered alongside or as
OL,21,Fan alternative to HRT".
