OL,3,CWhat is HRT and why is advice around
OL,4,Cmenopause treatment changing?
OL,6,FThe draft guidance said medics should
OL,7,F"consider CBT" for difficulties
OL,8,Fsleeping, depression and sleep
OL,9,Fproblems linked to menopause.
OL,11,FThe new updated guidance now says CBT
OL,12,Fcan be suitable as an add-on treatment
OL,13,Fto HRT, or for those who do not want
OL,14,For cannot take HRT.
OL,16,FNice has also emphasised in the
OL,17,Fupdated guideline that HRT does not
OL,18,Faffect overall life expectancy and
OL,19,Fwill not shorten or extend women's
OL,20,Flives.
